dct_description_sm: Survey of Egypt. Relief shown by 30 meters contours interval, gradient tints, and spot heights. Distance shown on map margins are in kilometer. Shows: railways (2 categories), roads (2 categories), tracks, canals. Relief shown by 30 metres contours interval and gradient tints. Distance shown on map margins are in kilometer.
